Maya The Bee, Episode 12 - Dancing With Bees

Series Synopsis

A fun-filled, 3D animated adventure series following Maya, a young bee who has left her hive to discover the beauty and mysteries of nature. Maya explores the meadows, meets other insects and shares her joy with her friends.

Episode Synopsis

Episode 12 - Dancing With Bees

Maya finds it very difficult learning the bees dance. Flip will try to help her and thanks to his lessons, Maya will be able to show the chief worker bee a new field of flowers that will help feed the larvae brood.
